    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Daomei Village</strong></h2><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/ed8501fdea3cb55c9fc99e09a09324d2.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br>Daomei Village  是一款可爱的像素风格游戏，背景设定在激发创造力的大气环境中！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/18b40aab8c6cfa4a3a43748123395126.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=81 /></span><br>奉天皇之命，你被流放到 Daomei Village，并被委派将其修复至完美的状态。请记住，任何事情都不会逃脱税吏的注意，他们会要求你向皇上进贡。你必须照顾农场、耕种田地、饲养动物和创造收入。一开始并不容易，因为你只有几个简单的工具、100元、一些稻子和一些茶。别放弃！一场奇妙的冒险正在等着你。你将会遇到和你一样因犯罪而被流放至 Daomei Village 的朋友。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/db7eac270fb5ae83bbdfe67384116358.poster.avif?t=1769669812\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/db7eac270fb5ae83bbdfe67384116358.webm?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/db7eac270fb5ae83bbdfe67384116358.mp4?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/175b4d6ce3f1b4c6658038e9f10edff3.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=84 /></span><br>季节变化影响种植蔬菜和花卉的可能性，每种动物都需要专门的空间。来吧，创造你梦想中的地方——田野、建筑物和环境，你可以创造和改善这一切。引进农作物自动化技术，美化区域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/f5d052ede87bbe18bef1b5ec3875f960.poster.avif?t=1769669812\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/f5d052ede87bbe18bef1b5ec3875f960.webm?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/f5d052ede87bbe18bef1b5ec3875f960.mp4?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/8db90235902758105f3f078b723dbe36.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=96 /></span><br>村里的活动会给你带来快乐和认可。平静下来的皇上将允许你前往帝国军队占领的敌人的土地。因此，你将获得有关新技术的信息、原材料、工具和种子。地形越困难，获得独特成就的机会就越大。你在探险中得到的一切都是你的，可以用来建造你的村庄。你是村庄的领袖。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/9aee9b91158d3fa613176c8f26760fc5.poster.avif?t=1769669812\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/9aee9b91158d3fa613176c8f26760fc5.webm?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/9aee9b91158d3fa613176c8f26760fc5.mp4?t=1769669812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/d6de7dacff09f017566c60af810b582f.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=108 /></span><br>村子里的每个人都做错了事。与村民互动时，你将获得有助于你获得他们信任的任务。你将会了解到他们因做了什么而被谴责流放。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825030/extras/2cd12d63719c57c61ce32d2ff4d40b76.avif?t=1769669812\" width=616 height=135 /></span><br>Daomei Village 是一个绝对独一无二的神奇地方。你会遇到历代的痕迹，了解独特的中国民间传说和妖怪学。你和居民将根据各自的生日和中国历法庆祝假期。你不能错过它！",
